    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un augſchup bija tam weena Dobbite weena Ohlektſ lee-\nla/ un ta Dobbite bija itt appa-\nſa padarrita no putſohtr Ohlek-\ntini/ un tai paſchâ Dobbitê bija\niſrakſtitas Bitdes/ un (wiſſo\nSkrahgo) Sahnû Galdi bija\ntſchetrfkantigi/ un ne appati-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee tſchetri Ritteni bi-\nja appaſſch teem Sahnû Gal-\ndeem/ un to Rittenu Affis bija\npee teem Skrahgeem/ un weens\nRittens bija putſohtr Ohlektſ\naugſts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Skritteſu Darbs\nbija ta patt ta Rattu-Skritteſi/\nwinnu Affis/ un winnu Mut-\ntuti/ un winnu Speeki/ un win-\nnu Wainagi bija wiſſi leeti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee tſchetri Turramee\nbija us teem tſchetreem Stuh-\nreem ikweena Skrahga/ un is-\nſteepeahs no ta Skrahga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un augſcham us to Skrah-\ngi bija weens appaſſch Stab-\nbinsch puſs Ohlektſ Augſtumâ\napfahrt/ un augſcham us to\nSkrahgi bija arridsan winna\nOhſchi/ un winna Turramee is-\nſteepeahs no winna:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſch greese us win-\nna Ohſchu Sahneem/ un us win-\nna Turrameem/ Kerubim/ Lau-\nwas un Palma-Rohkus/ ta ta ik-\nkatram Weetas bija/ un Glib-\ntumi bija apfahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta darrija wiſſch Skrah-\ngus weenada leeta Darba/ teem\nbij weenahds Mehrs/ weenada\nIſrakſtischana bija teem wiſſeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſch darrija arridsan\ndesmits Warra Katlus/ weenâ\nKatlâ ſagahje tſchetrdemits\nBatti/ weens Katlis bija tſchet-\nras Ohlektis leels/ us ikkatru\nSkrahgi no teem desmits\nSkrahgeem bija weenis Katlis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch likke peeſus no\nteem Skrahgeem pa labbas Puſ-\nfes ta Namma/ un peeſas likke\nwiſſch pa kreitas Namma Puſ-\nfes/ bet to Juhrn likke wiſſch pa\nlabbas Puſſes ta Namma us\nPreeſchu prettDeenas-Widdus-\npuffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irans darrija arridsan\nPohdus/ Lahpſtas/ un Beſke-\nnus/ un Irans pabeidſe wiſſu\nto Darbu/ ko wiſſch tam keh-\nniam Salamanam darrija\npreekſch ta KUNGA Namnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "(Prohti) tohs diwi Stab-\nbus/ un appaſſas Pohgas us\nteem diwi Stabbeem/ un tahs-\ndiwi pihtas Stihpas/ kas tahs-\ndiwi appaſſas Pohgas apſedſe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tohs tſchetrfints Gra-\nnata-Ahbotus pee tahm diwi\npihtahmStihpahm/(prohti) di-\nwi Rindas Granata-Ahbotu pee\nweenas Stihpas/ kas tahs diwi\nappaſſas Pohgas us teem Stab-\nbeem apſedſe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lihds ar teem desmits\nSkrahgeem/ un ar teem desmits\nKatleem Skrahgu Wirſii.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir to weenn Juhrn/ un\ntohs diwipadesmits Wehrthue-\nappaſſch tahs Juhras.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir tohs Pohdus un Lahp-\nſtas/\n"
    }
  ],
